🧯 Debug / Issue with Prompt (Prompt Rescue) ⌄
  • Identify failure modes: hallucination, drift, bias, inconsistency.
  • Rewrite with structure: roles, constraints, checks, chain‑of‑thought controls.
  • Few‑shot libraries & retrieval grounding for accuracy.
  • Red‑teaming + regression suites to lock reliability.
🧪 VEO Design & Evaluation ⌄
